data.description: Back on the Market at no fault of the seller! Charming and better than new! This entire house has been renovated! We're talking all new windows, smart siding, heat/air unit w/ new duct work, roof, all the flooring, both the kitchen & bath were completely redone which includes a walk-in tile shower, granite countertop, backsplash, upgraded kitchen appliances & cabinetry, interior doors, tankless water heater, all the plumbing & wiring--it has all been done for you! The backyard has an above ground pool, fenced off area for the dogs, plus a large storage building. Close to downtown & walking trails. Call to see this one today!
